Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.36,0:52:54.36,English,,0,0,0,,That sort of like trap hot air.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.28,0:52:58.16,English,,0,0,0,,People live for a very long time.\N{\rChinese}人们寿命很长。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.32,0:53:02.12,English,,0,0,0,,I think over half of the population will live past 55,\N{\rChinese}我想大约一半人口会活到55岁以上，
