Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.36,0:53:27.12,English,,0,0,0,,So, the reason why they're so different is because they're so different from Egypt and Mesopotamia, okay, because again, Egypt, it's a centralized empire.\N{\rChinese}所以，原因是因为它们与埃及和美索不太相同，先后…
